<% page_title :pages_training_hub %>
<% content_for :breadcrumb do
    generate_breadcrumbs(
      t('breadcrumb.training_hub'),
      [
        [t('breadcrumb.task_list_home'), task_list_path]
      ]
    )
  end
%>

<div class="govuk-grid-row govuk-!-margin-top-7 govuk-body">
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds govuk-!-margin-bottom-7">
    <h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">Find training that boosts your job options</h1>
    <p class="govuk-body-l">You could get a better job by adding to the skills you already have. Complete a short course in maths or English and you could find you have a wider range of job options. Many courses are free and offer flexible times to fit round your life.</p>
    <p class="govuk-body-l">This is a new scheme - a wider range of courses will be added in future.</p>
    <p class="govuk-body-l">You can also find on-the-job training that lets you earn while you learn.</p>
    <h2 class="govuk-heading-l">Whatâ€™s on offer?</h2>
    <%= render 'shared/training_hub/maths' %>
    <%= render 'shared/training_hub/english' %>
    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">On-the-job training</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Gain skills and experience while continuing to earn. There's no age limit and different levels of study are available. This means on-the-job-training is suitable for experienced older workers wanting to stay in work as they learn.</p>
    <%= link_to('Find an opportunity', 'https://www.gov.uk/apprenticeships-guide', class: 'govuk-button govuk-!-margin-top-5 govuk-button govuk-!-margin-bottom-2', target: '_blank', data: { tracked_event: "Training hub - Clicked 'Find an opportunity': https://www.gov.uk/apprenticeships-guide" }) %>
    <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--m govuk-section-break--visible">
    <h2 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">More help to change jobs</h2>
    <p class="govuk-body-m govuk-!-margin-bottom-1">Get support to find and apply for jobs, or find other ways to move into a new role.</p>
    <%= link_to('Other ways to change jobs', next_steps_path, class: 'govuk-button govuk-!-margin-top-5 govuk-button govuk-!-margin-bottom-2') %>
    <hr class="govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--m govuk-section-break--visible">
  </div>
  <%= render "shared/contact_us" %>
  <%= render 'shared/save_or_return_to_your_results' %>
  <%= render 'shared/help_improve_this_service' %>
</div>
